name: Secret AXE ME VR Pre Alpha Test
name_original: Secret AXE ME VR Pre Alpha Test
description: It's a pre alpha test of my axe throwing VR game. This version is  a no frills, mechanics only, bare bones test. This is more of a, does it work on someone else's computer than mine kind of test. Still, it should be fun axe throwing! Get to 21 and  it cheers. Try and hit an orange and the target at the same time if you want.
